<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/231116-what-happened-to-bill-toy-i-know-he-died">What happened to Bill Toy? I know he died, but does the book clue us in as to why or how?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_231116'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F34605.The_Damnation_Game">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/231116-what-happened-to-bill-toy-i-know-he-died">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/231116-what-happened-to-bill-toy-i-know-he-died">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/9605563-stephen-newton"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1341071339i/9605563._UY100_CR2,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/9605563-stephen-newton">Stephen Newton</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    The book does explain why (When Whitehead explains his relationship to Mamoulian to Marty he explains how they both assaulted Mamoulian when he cast a<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    The book does explain why (When Whitehead explains his relationship to Mamoulian to Marty he explains how they both assaulted Mamoulian when he cast aside). It doesn’t explain how. The last we see of Toy is when he’s fleeing his house being chased by The Razor Eater, and then it’s inferred that Marty hears him crying in the casino washroom. After that, everyone just talks about him being dead.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

