<span id="freeTextContainer16324913978702241645">By far my favorite of Barker&apos;s novels, this Faustian tale of a man caught in a battle between evil and more evil is just begging for a screen adaptation. Scary and thoughtful, The Damnation Game will stay with you a long time.</span>
  <span id="freeText16324913978702241645" style="display:none">By far my favorite of Barker's novels, this Faustian tale of a man caught in a battle between evil and more evil is just begging for a screen adaptation. Scary and thoughtful, The Damnation Game will stay with you a long time.</span>
